<hgroup class="visually-hidden">
  <h1>Welcome to MarkGodi.com</h1>
  <p>Teacher | Author | Speaker | WASC Coordinator</p>
</hgroup>

<div class="columns" id="introduction">
  <div class="image">
    <div class="profile-pic-wrapper yellow">
      <img src="/profile_pic.jpg" alt="Mark Godi" class="profile-pic" />
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="intro">
    <h2>Hi, I'm Mark!</h2>
    <p class="lead">
      Teacher, Author, Speaker, WASC Coordinator...<br class="keep-break" />and
      the person called when accreditation is on the line<br /> and uncertainty is
      winning.
    </p>

    <hr />

    <p>
      I offer workshops, keynotes, and coaching for schools, districts, and
      organizations. My work is focused on helping educators and leaders build
      sustainable, student-centered learning environments that prioritize depth,
      relationships, and real growth over hustle culture.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you’re ready to bring workshops, keynotes, or coaching to your campus
      or district, let’s talk.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .columns {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: left;
    margin-inline: auto;
    margin-block: 3rem 0rem;
  }

  br:not(.keep-break) {
    display: none;
  }

  @media (min-width: 120ch) {
    .columns {
      flex-direction: row;
      align-items: flex-start;
      text-align: flex-start;
      gap: 3rem;
      margin-block: 5rem 2rem;
    }

    br:not(.keep-break) {
      display: block;
    }
  }

  .intro {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .intro h2 {
    font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 5vw, 5rem);
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-block: 0 2rem;
    color: #244057;
    text-align: center;
  }

  @media (min-width: 120ch) {
    .intro h2 {
      text-align: start;
      margin-block: 5rem 2rem;
    }
  }

  .intro p.lead {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-block: 0 2rem;
    font-family: "EB Garamond", serif;
    text-align: center;
  }

  @media (min-width: 120ch) {
    .intro p.lead {
      text-align: start;
      margin-block: 0 3rem;
    }
  }

  .intro p:not(.lead) {
    max-width: 70ch;
  }
